        <Parent_String>stone by function [300011699], stone (worked rock) [300011176], rock by form [300201479], rock (inorganic material) [300011692], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
